Ruben, thanks!  I'm about to board a plane and will not have time for further tests.  If you feel like it, please jump in and fix any mistakes that you may find!

This seems like a reasonable approach to take. I guess the previous version wasn't working because after the first `mk_all` was run, the second one was just checking that output!

When you're back please run any other tests you were thinking of and then merge. Thanks!
bors d+
